data.description: Gorgeous 4 bed 3 full bath home with tons of space and great layout. Also has a basement. Kitchen is good size and has nice eat in area. Grand foyer and family room with full bath downstairs and 2 upstairs. Huge master suite with great master bath as well. 3rd story is 4th bedroom and has lots of space there too. Come check this one out it will not last long.
